      <p>You covered the OWASP web vulnerability landscape end-to-end: info disclosure, broken authn/authz, injection, XSS, SSRF, prompt injection, and JWT misconfig. Real engagements look exactly like this. Chain small wins, recognize patterns, write them up.</p>
